EvxoI"><img alt="a happy leave me alone user" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/Grace-McCarter-95e3da390707310a7c72aaf1aa2b39c7.jpg" loading="lazy"></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--content--m9voa"><p class="wall-of-love-module--text--RZ+ih"><span>I'm one of those people who loves a clean slate – but unfortunately, I also love signing up to mailing lists. After five simple minutes reviewing my subscription choices alongside the emails sliding into my inbox without permission, <span class="text-module--highlight--s-Wxt ">my email inbox remains a productive – not distracting – place to visit. Invaluable</span>.</span></p><div class="wall-of-love-module--name-container--Wjqwx"><a href="https://twitter.com/GraceMcCarter" class="wall-of-love-module--twitter-link--VsY4F"><span class="wall-of-love-module--name--f+n2O">Grace McCarter</span></a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="wall-of-love-module--wrapper--GeBtG"><div class="wall-of-love-module--box--L99pF"><div class="wall-of-love-module--img--EvxoI"><img alt="a happy leave me alone user" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/AC-Dye-755924c0363c75aab07136a12a75492a.jpg" loading="lazy"></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--content--m9voa"><p class="wall-of-love-module--text--RZ+ih"><span><span class="text-module--highlight--s-Wxt ">Leave Me Alone is such an easy to use tool</span>, and I love supporting indie founders. Danielle and James are active on Twitter, and they are always ready to help any way they can.</span></p><div class="wall-of-love-module--name-container--Wjqwx"><a href="https://twitter.com/acdyee" class="wall-of-love-module--twitter-link--VsY4F"><span class="wall-of-love-module--name--f+n2O">AC Dye</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--wrapper--GeBtG"><div class="wall-of-love-module--box--L99pF"><div class="wall-of-love-module--img--EvxoI"><img alt="a happy leave me alone user" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/Dominic-Monn-33b6535cb70c0a68091f3e83c6c511d8.jpg" loading="lazy"></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--content--m9voa"><p class="wall-of-love-module--text--RZ+ih"><span>Leave Me Alone has helped me make my inbox tidy again! An amazing product that is <span class="text-module--highlight--s-Wxt ">affordable, fast and easy</span>.</span></p><div class="wall-of-love-module--name-container--Wjqwx"><a href="https://twitter.com/dqmonn" class="wall-of-love-module--twitter-link--VsY4F"><span class="wall-of-love-module--name--f+n2O">Dominic Monn</span></a><div class="wall-of-love-module--company-container--TTyxJ"><img class="wall-of-love-module--company-logo--MEaE3" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/mentor-cruise-a498b9f96398ac239632f249e754de49.jpg" alt="" role="presentation" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="wall-of-love-module--wrapper--GeBtG"><div class="wall-of-love-module--box--L99pF"><div class="wall-of-love-module--img--EvxoI"><img alt="a happy leave me alone user" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/Amie-Chen-26947c46fa9ce1ab4fd0f2d5de86239a.jpg" loading="lazy"></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--content--m9voa"><p class="wall-of-love-module--text--RZ+ih"><span>The attention to detail of Leave Me Alone is awesome! Not only does it work great but it is also well designed. The overall experience is very welcoming and smooth -- <span class="text-module--highlight--s-Wxt ">I especially love the quality score of each email address.</span> This tool made unsubscribing emails so addictive!</span></p><div class="wall-of-love-module--name-container--Wjqwx"><a href="https://twitter.com/hyper_yolo" class="wall-of-love-module--twitter-link--VsY4F"><span class="wall-of-love-module--name--f+n2O">Amie Chen</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--wrapper--GeBtG"><div class="wall-of-love-module--box--L99pF"><div class="wall-of-love-module--img--EvxoI"><img alt="a happy leave me alone user" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/Dinuka-cfb855c9a3fc0f976078bdc6a473e56f.jpg" loading="lazy"></div><div class="wall-of-love-module--content--m9voa"><p class="wall-of-love-module--text--RZ+ih"><span>Leave Me Alone helped me <span class="text-module--highlight--s-Wxt ">clean out all the spam and email subscriptions that I've been avoiding</span> and reduced the burden on checking emails every day!</span></p><div class="wall-of-love-module--name-container--Wjqwx"><a href="https://twitter.com/dinuka_jay" class="wall-of-love-module--twitter-link--VsY4F"><span class="wall-of-love-module--name--f+n2O">Dinuka</span></a><div class="wall-of-love-module--company-container--TTyxJ"><img class="wall-of-love-module--company-logo--MEaE3" src="https://cdn-a.leavemealone.app/static/tutorseek-c492b0dc000b0f3743750e34c9edc872.jpg" alt="" role="presentation" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
